---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = 'Privacy Policy — 1099 Estimator';
const description = '1099 Estimator privacy policy. Your tax inputs are processed entirely in your browser and never sent to or stored on our servers.';
const updated = 'June 2, 2026';
---
<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-14">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">The short version</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Your calculator inputs — your income, expenses, and filing status — are processed <b>entirely within your own web browser</b>. They are never transmitted to, collected by, or stored on our servers. We have no account system and never ask for personally identifying financial information.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Information we collect</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We do not collect the figures you enter into the calculator. Like most websites, we may collect limited, non-identifying technical information automatically — such as your browser type, device type, and pages visited — to understand aggregate usage and keep the site working.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Cookies and analytics</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We may use privacy-respecting analytics to measure aggregate traffic. If we display advertising in the future, our advertising partners (such as Google) may use cookies to serve and measure ads. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your visit to this and other sites. You can opt out of personalized advertising via <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-indigo-600 underline">Google Ads Settings</a>.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Third-party services</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Any third-party services we use (for hosting, analytics, or advertising) have their own privacy policies governing how they handle data. We encourage you to review them. This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Children's privacy</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">This site is intended for adults managing their own taxes and is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be reflected by the "last updated" date above.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:hello@1099estimator.com" class="text-indigo-600 underline">hello@1099estimator.com</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>
